Author: beccabitesback
Text: Owning the DSM 5 book, I can say that it is absolutely as bad as any other eating disorder, especially when seen at different extremes. In the book it states possible symptoms for all disorders and, along with anorexia and bulimia, BED has its own list of issues that stem from it.  Your eating disorder is valid and youâ€™re strong for acknowledging it.
